@{PARD}
@{B}Ghost, Green Combat:@{UB}@{PAR}

Green ghosts are not undead, therefore, they cannot be turned by
Priests. They attack with two claws, doing 1-6 points of damage with each
successful hit. They have a limited resistance to magic.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

