@{PARD}
@{B}Ghost, Green Ecology:@{UB}@{PAR}

It is believed that Green Ghosts are not native to the prime material
plane, and therefore have no place in nature. Green Ghosts never need to eat,
sleep, drink or rest.@{PAR}

